Use a mortar and pestle to grind the @shiitake_mushroms{4} and @bouillon_cube{2}. 
Add them to @hot_water{0.5%cup}, along with the @sugar{1%tsp}, @five_spice_powder{1%tsp}. 

While that mixture is soaking, heat up @oil{0.33%cups}. Fry @galangal{1%inch} and @shallot{1}. Then add @navy_beans{1%can}, @sweet_chili_sauce{2%tbsp}, @dark_chinese_vinegar{2%tbsp}, and @sichuan_peppercorn{4%tsp}. Heat until thickened. 